Description: Here is a super cool vintage Fernandes Stratocaster that has been hooked up to ROCK OUT! It has been set up with vintage dirty finger/zebra hubucking pickups and only knob... that's right the volume knob. It's a no thrills all kills tone monster that is a great way to add some vintage tone and serious mojo to your arsenal for a player friendly price. It's a guitar you can beat up and play with no worries. It's in great shape for it's age and is also super light weight thanks to the humbucker routes. At one point it had a locking nut but its back to normal now. The neck is straight and the frets are in good shape as well. This guitar has a nice thin finish and big rock tones.
